        <h1>Roofing in Dromana</h1>
        <p>We provide expert <strong>roof repairs, restorations, re-roofing and roof painting</strong> across Dromana and surrounding suburbs. Our materials and coatings are chosen for Peninsula coastal conditions and installed to Australian Standards.</p>
        
        <p>Dromana's central Peninsula location presents unique roofing challenges, from salt air exposure to variable coastal weather patterns. Our team understands these local conditions, having serviced the area's mix of holiday homes, family residences, and historic properties for over 25 years. We're familiar with the suburb's diverse architectural styles – from the classic beach houses near the pier to modern developments around the Dromana shopping precinct.</p>
        
        <p>Whether you're dealing with storm damage from Peninsula weather, require maintenance on a coastal property, or planning a seaside renovation, we provide tailored solutions. Our local knowledge extends to council requirements, coastal building standards, and the specific materials that perform best in Dromana's seaside environment. We service all areas including Point Nepean Road, Pier Street, and the residential streets around Dromana Primary School.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Leak detection & roof repairs</li>
          <li>Full roof restorations & coatings</li>
          <li>Tile or metal re-roofing</li>
          <li>Professional roof painting</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="btn-row">
